name: Emuwa
description: I want to let everyone on here knows that I am not here for games. If you are here for games, please get off me. I can be very interesting and adventurous. Life is cool and beautiful to live in only when you are with the right set of people. I need a good companion to go along with and want to be friends first and see what comes out of it. If you are ready to learn and live along too, reach me and lets see how the heart clicks. Lets enjoy the grace of his eternal living together in his love and kindness.
